        "label": "Lesson 7 • Discussing bad results",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Ron, Alex, and Pam work for Brooklyn Brewski, a company that brews and distributes beer throughout New York. The company’s recent results have been terrible."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Alex: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We need to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"face the music"
            },
            {
              "text":	" here. We’re "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"in deep trouble"
            },
            {
              "text":	"! Sales are down by 50 percent versus last year."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Pam: "
            },
            {
              "text": "It looks like we’re going to be "
            },
            {
              "markedtext":	"in the red"
            },
            {
              "text":	" for the year "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"to the tune of"
            },
            {
              "text":	" $1 million."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Ron: "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "No wonder"
            },
            {
              "text":	". We’re losing "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"market share"
            },
            {
              "text":	" to Manhattan Beer."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Alex: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Why? We need to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"get to the bottom of this"
            },
            {
              "text":	"!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Pam: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Every year they come up with new beers. They’re really "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"on top of trends"
            },
            {
              "text":	". For instance, last year they released a low-carb beer."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Ron: "
            },
            {
              "text": "No wonder they’re "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"eating our lunch"
            },
            {
              "text":	"! They’re "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"cashing in on"
            },
            {
              "text":	" the latest trends and bringing "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"great new products to market"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Pam: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Meanwhile, we’re "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"running in place"
            },
            {
              "text":	". We need a new product line and new ideas for marketing."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Alex: "
            },
            {
              "text": "It’s time to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"clean house"
            },
            {
              "text":	" and bring some"
            },
            {
              "markedText":	" new blood"
            },
            {
              "text":	" into this company."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Ron: "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "You took the words right out of my mouth"
            },
            {
              "text":	"! We need some new people with fresh ideas."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
